text: Debden is a village and civil parish in Uttlesford, Essex, England. It is located 4 miles (6 km) from Saffron Walden and 17 miles (27 km) from Cambridge. In 2001 there were 753 people living in Debden.ONS == References == Category:Villages in Essex Category:Civil parishes in Essex Category:Uttlesford
